::GoldenEye/ Kitkat::

GoldenEye::
She watched him put Dollen into the CR chamber.  She stood by the 
chamber and waited for him to get out.  She took a few steps closer 
to the chamber. She whispered,"Please come out of there in good 
condition." She lowered her head and prayed to the Matrix for him.

KitKat:;
She looked up from her desk at Drillbit.  Her cheeks were tear 
stained and her eyes were bloodshot from crying.  She looked at him 
with the pain in her spark showing. She whispered,"I'm sorry." was 
all she could say.  She choked, lowered her head back down, and wept.

> ::DrillBit::
> 
> Now at the base, DrillBit climbed through the hatch, and then helped
> Dollen and GoldenEye through. He helped carry Dollen to the CR tank.
> "Here we are." He said, lifting the bot into the tank.
> He then ran back to KitKat.
> "Honey, do you want to talk?" He asked.
